rw suggested input in the minibuffer.
[http://www.marcelotoledo.org/pub/stuff/screenshots/erc-minibuffer.jpg
here] is a screen shot.

You need to set the variable `erc-prompt-interactive-input' to t to
get this feature.

Note: This above mentioned variable has been removed from ERC (as of erc.el CVS revision 1.601).

